        "language_selected": "\nthe application will be displayed in English.",
        "UnknownError": "An unknown error occurred during the operation. \ndescription: {e}",
        "delay_question":  "how many seconds do you want between each message? \n\n",
        "__version__": "\n\ncurrent version: '{version}'",
        "different_msg_question":  "\n\nEnter how many different messages you will send {limits}. \n\nNOTE: you are NOT being asked how many times a message will be sent, but how many DIFFERENT messages will be sent.\nyou will choose how many times each one will be sent later. \n\nthis many different messages will be sent: ",
        "list_commands": "\n\ninvalid input. only the following inputs are valid at this point: \n\n\ta number within limits: \n\t\tdetermines how many different messages will be sent and continues. \n\tsaves: \n\t\tshows saved registry entries and lets you load one. \n\tversion: \n\t\tshows the current version. \n\texit/quit: \n\t\tcloses the program. \n\tdelete: \n\t\tdeletes the registry main key and its contents created by the program. \n\n",
        "amount_question": "amount: ",
        "start":  "\n\nGET READY, SPAM IS STARTING AND YOU HAVE \"{waiting_period}\" SECONDS BEFORE IT BEGINS!!!!\n\n",
        "writing_amount_question":  "\nyou selected all your messages. now you need to choose \nhow many times each message will be sent in total. \n\neach message will be sent this many times {limits}: ",
        "start_delay_question":  "\nnow when you press enter, you must choose how many seconds later \nthe spam will start. \n\nI will have this much time {limits}: ",
        "ready_txt": "\neverything is ready. once you press \"ENTER\" \nyou will have \"{waiting_period}\" seconds before a total of \"{total_msg}\" messages rain down.\n",
