        "msg_preparation": "\nwe will ask you what will be written in each message, there will be a total of \"{different_msg_amount}\" questions.",
        "quit_txt": "you chose not to continue. exiting...",
        "invalid_option": "\n\nplease enter a valid option\n\n",
        "reg_save_question": "you can save the spam that just occurred to the registry and quickly access it next time. \ndo you want this? \n\nY/YES : yes, save the current spam.\nN/NO  : no, do not save the current spam. \n\nyour choice: ",
        "again_question": "\n\ndo you want another round with the same messages?\n\nY/YES : yes, restart the same loop. \nN/NO  : no, close the program. \n\nyour choice: "
